message.body: Hey Nate. I think I mentioned I'll be dog-sitting for Lincoln in a few weeks. It falls on Valentines Day weekend. I'm working a double on Sat, Feb 14th and brunch on the Sun, Feb 15th. I need someone to do a lunch walk for Lincoln on Sat and Sun and a dinner walk & feeding on Sat night. You able to do any or all of those? On a separate note, how you feeling? Any better?
Sorry I haven't gotten back to you.
I'm not sure yet if I can do it
